Package: connections
Title: Generic Database Package Integration with the 'RStudio' Connections Pane and 'pins'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Edgar", "Ruiz", email = "edgar@rstudio.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a generic integration with the 'RStudio' connections pane, and the 'pins' package. 
  It is meant to be used with 'DBI' compliant connection packages.
License: GPL-3
